PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,FResidents in Whitstable in Kent have
OL,7,Ftaken to bathing in the sea as they
OL,8,Fendure a seventh day without water
OL,9,Fduring the heatwave.
OL,11,FThe group gathered on Whitstable beach
OL,12,Fon Friday morning to wash and brush
OL,13,Ftheir teeth in the ocean, after being
OL,14,Fleft for a week with no supplies
OL,15,Fbecause storage reservoirs for the
OL,16,Farea "reached a critical level".
OL,18,FLocals have described the latest
OL,19,Foutage as "a crisis" and say it poses
OL,20,Fa health and safety risk.
OL,26,@xD@FOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, organiser
OL,7,FCaroline Wade said: "While everyone is
OL,8,Fhaving fun in the sea today and
OL,9,Fwashing, the real message is we
OL,10,Fhaven't got any water at home.
OL,12,F"There's no water for flushing our
OL,13,Ftoilets, no water for bathing, no
OL,14,Fwater for cleaning dirty plates and
OL,15,Fdishes and no water to drink.
OL,17,F"We need the government to take this
OL,18,Fseriously now - we want South East
OL,19,FWater and the rest of the water
OL,20,Fcompanies nationalised, as they're
OL,21,Fobviously not up to purpose.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"Water is not a luxury, it's a daily
OL,7,Fessential that everyone needs and it's
OL,8,Fa health and safety risk, frankly, in
OL,9,Fa heatwave."
OL,11,FResident Karen Bayfield joined the
OL,12,Fbathing and said her family have had
OL,13,Fno water for two days.
OL,15,F"It's crazy," she said.
OL,17,F"My husband's a builder, so washing,
OL,18,Fdrinking, everyday life, really, has
OL,19,Fbeen affected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"South East Water keep saying that
OL,7,Fthey can't get water to higher levels,
OL,8,Fbut we're actually at sea level.
OL,10,F"So I can't quite see where that
OL,11,Fargument's going.
OL,13,F"There's too much housing going on
OL,14,Faround this area - the infrastructure
OL,15,Fisn't here.
OL,17,F"It's just a nightmare."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,FSouth East Water said around 3,500
OL,7,Fcustomers are still without supplies
OL,8,Fon Friday, but that they are doing
OL,9,Feverything they can to get treated
OL,10,Fwater into the reservoirs.
OL,12,FBut though some customers will see
OL,13,Ftheir taps running today, others could
OL,14,Fhave intermittent supplies all weekend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
