OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,FThe company's Incident Manager, Steve
OL,7,FBenton, said: "We are starting to see
OL,8,Ftap water supplies returning to some
OL,9,Fcustomers across Kent, however some
OL,10,Fare still experiencing water supply
OL,11,Fissues as a result of incredibly high
OL,12,Fdemand during this heatwave.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"Yesterday (Thursday 28 May) we pumped
OL,7,F619 million litres of water to
OL,8,Fcustomers across our region. This
OL,9,Fcontinues to be higher than the
OL,10,Faverage for this time of year. On some
OL,11,Fdays during this period of high
OL,12,Fdemand, we have treated and pumped
OL,13,Faround 100 million litres more than
OL,14,Fthe daily average for May.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"We are doing everything we can to get
OL,7,Ftreated water into our storage
OL,8,Freservoirs, including using our
OL,9,Ftankers to support the network and
OL,10,Fensuring all available treatment works
OL,11,Fare running at full capacity. However,
OL,12,Fsome customers will continue to have
OL,13,Fintermittent water supply until these
OL,14,Flevels have been restored. This means
OL,15,Fwater may be on and off throughout the
OL,16,Fday.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"Parts of Whitstable saw supplies
OL,7,Freturning last night. Currently there
OL,8,Fare around 3,500 customers without
OL,9,Fsupply in the Whitstable area, but
OL,10,Fthis is expected to start returning
OL,11,Flater today. Tap water is likely to
OL,12,Fremain intermittent across the weekend
OL,13,Ffor all customers in this area.
OL,15,F"Around 200 customers in Cranbrook are
OL,16,Fcurrently without supply. This is
OL,17,Fbecause the drinking water storage
OL,18,Ftanks which serve these areas have
OL,19,Freached a critical level.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"In addition, there are currently
OL,7,Faround 8,700 customers experiencing
OL,8,Flow pressure or an intermittent supply
OL,9,Fin Ulcombe, Coxheath, Loose, Headcorn,
OL,10,FHerne Bay, Charing, Challock and
OL,11,FMolash.
OL,13,F"In areas where there has been supply
OL,14,Finterruption - or where we believe
OL,15,Fissues may occur - we're delivering
OL,16,Fbottled water to our vulnerable
OL,17,Fcustomers on our Priority Services
OL,18,FRegister.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"We have delivered 229,464 litres of
OL,7,Fwater to customers on our Priority
OL,8,FServices Register and also delivered
OL,9,Fbottled water to critical care
OL,10,Fsettings such as care homes, GP
OL,11,Fsurgeries, pharmacies and dentists.
OL,13,F"Our fleet of tankers has been working
OL,14,F24/7 putting an extra one million
OL,15,Flitres of water into the network in
OL,16,Fareas where demand has been extremely
OL,17,Fhigh and to support our stored water
OL,18,Freservoirs. So far, we have tankered
OL,19,Fover 1,753,561 litres of water into
OL,20,Fthe network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"We have also given out 283,884
OL,7,Fbottles of water at our bottled water
OL,8,Fstations across Kent and continue to
OL,9,Fidentify new locations for other
OL,10,Fstations to open.
OL,12,F"Additionally, we are supporting the
OL,13,FQueen Victoria Memorial Hospital in
OL,14,FHerne Bay and urgent care unit with a
OL,15,Ftanker and supporting those with
OL,16,Flivestock.
OL,18,F"We are continuing to ask customers in
OL,19,Fsupply to use water for essential
OL,20,Fpurposes only - for example drinking,
OL,21,Fwashing and cooking.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"We have bottled water collection
OL,7,Fstations already set up and are
OL,8,Freviewing these locations continuously.
OL,10,F"Our call centre is experiencing high
OL,11,Fcall volumes. Customers can find FAQs,
OL,12,Fdetails of bottled water stations and
OL,13,Finformation about locations currently
OL,14,Fexperiencing supply issues via our
OL,15,Fwebsite.
OL,17,F"We are sorry to customers who have
OL,18,Fhad interruptions or low pressure in
OL,19,Ftheir water supply and know how
OL,20,Ffrustrating it is, especially in very
OL,21,Fhot weather.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
