PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780138973
OL,3,CPeople left with no running water wash
OL,4,Cand brush their teeth in the sea
OL,6,F"We will continue to do all we can to
OL,7,Fprevent and resolve the issues.
OL,9,F"For updates, please visit
OL,10,Faqualerter.southeastwater.co. uk"
